# Features to be implemented in version 1.0:

* Modularity
* GUI
* ECTS distribution according to the official documentation
* Configuration file
* AUTHORS file
* BSD License
* Logging system
* Setting up limits for F and FX ranges
* Working with buffer
* Working with marks, distributions and deviations
* Showing deviations by algorithms
* Configuring the "National ECTS" ranging

# Features planned in version 1.1:

* Authentification system
* Updating system
* Auto-updating
* Database support for collecting marks
* Multilingual support
* Import/export ws Excel, CSV, PDF, TXT, etc

# Features planned later:

* Loading data from network (JSON, probably)
* Web interface
* Hosting

